Patch the deployment so the DU BFF App Service receives these environment variables from Azure DevOps variable group/app settings:

BFF_OIDC_ISSUER
BFF_OIDC_CLIENT_ID
BFF_OIDC_CLIENT_SECRET
BFF_OIDC_REDIRECT_URI
BFF_OIDC_SCOPES
BFF_OIDC_AUDIENCE
BFF_OIDC_POST_LOGIN_REDIRECT
SESSION_MAX_AGE

Add the required Bicep params and add them into the duApiAppSettings properties block in infra/templates/web-app.bicep. Also update the pipeline parameter mapping if deploy.steps.yml passes variable group values into the Bicep deployment. Do not hardcode environment-specific values or secrets.


